transcript:
Customer: Hello.
Executive: Good afternoon sir ji.
Customer: Ji madam baat kara do jo account manager.
Executive: Account manager se to baat kara dungi aapne 96 number pe call kyu kiya sir?
Customer: Are madam us puchna tha kuch bare me na.
Executive: Nakul mera number hai directly mere number pe call kar sakte ho sir mujhe whatsapp kar sakte ho.
Customer: Chalo.
Executive: Ab fir wohi concern mujhe yaha pe update dena padega dobara se. Chalo chalo. Dusri baar. Chalo chalo kya hota hai sir do dusri baar aaya hai aapka concern ye.
Customer: Koi baat nahi. Close kar do.
summary:
Concerns:

- Customer wants to connect to the account manager.

- Customer had a query.



Resolution:

- Executive asked why customer called on 96 number.

- Executive informed customer to call/WhatsApp directly.



Next Steps: 

None



Alert (If Any):

None
